OL,3,CMore than #13,000 raised for Guernsey
OL,4,Cfisherman whose boat sank
OL,6,FMore than #13,000 has been raised for
OL,7,Fa Guernsey fisherman to repair his
OL,8,Fboat, after it capsized and sank.
OL,10,FHe was working alone off the east
OL,11,Fcoast of Sark on Tuesday 30 September,
OL,12,Fhauling in pots, when the equipment
OL,13,Fsnagged, causing his boat, Wild Wave,
OL,14,Fto capsize and sink.
OL,16,FThe community in the Bailiwick has
OL,17,Fsince come together to exceed the
OL,18,Finitial target of #10,000, which will
OL,19,Fbe used "to get Wild Wave back on the
OL,20,Fwater and catching lobsters".
