OL,6,FThe description on the Just Giving
OL,7,Fpage explains that the boat "will need
OL,8,Fall new electrics and wiring, new
OL,9,Fengine, new safety equipment".
OL,11,F"Unfortunately due to reasons beyond
OL,12,Fhis control, insuring wooden vessels
OL,13,Flike 'Wild Wave' fully comprehensive
OL,14,Fcan be difficult and very expensive."
OL,16,FCommercial diver Richard Keen, who was
OL,17,Fpart of the rescue, said: "We had lots
OL,18,Fof help, people wanted to come and
OL,19,Fhelp tow it, it's a crowd of fishermen
OL,20,Fhere. It's a community of people.
