OL,3,CMore than #13,000 raised for Guernsey
OL,4,Cfisherman whose boat sank
OL,6,F"Everyone wants to help a young
OL,7,Ffisherman in their moment of need,
OL,8,Feverybody gives their time for free.
OL,9,FIt's one of those things.
OL,11,F"We were all young once, and we all
OL,12,Fneeded a bit of help from somebody
OL,13,Fsometimes, and to us old pensioners,
OL,14,Fit doesn't matter.
OL,16,F"It's sad, one of the few young
OL,17,Ffishermen we have left. He's got his
OL,18,Fboat back, but it needs a major
OL,19,Frepair. He had just refitted it.
