OL,4,Cfisherman whose boat sank
OL,6,F"But he's safe, the boat's back, but
OL,7,Fit's a bit of a sad affair. I just
OL,8,Ffeel very sorry for him, he's got a
OL,9,Fyoung family, a seven-week-old baby,
OL,10,Fand you get fished out of the water."
OL,12,FThe Chief Inspector of Marine
OL,13,FAccidents has ordered a safety
OL,14,Finvestigation to identify what caused
OL,15,Fthe incident and to try to prevent
OL,16,Ffuture problems.
